msgctxt "392_Akiyama"
msgid "Ever heard of 777 Town?"
msgstr "¿Alguna vez has oído hablar de 777 Town?"

msgctxt "404_Erena"
msgid "777 Town? What's that?"
msgstr "¿777 Town? ¿Y eso qué es?"

msgctxt "416_Akiyama"
msgid "It's a game for your computer or cell phone. It lets you play pachinko and slots anytime, anywhere you want."
msgstr "Es un juego para el teléfono y la computadora. Te permite jugar al pachinko y a las tragamonedas en cualquier momento y lugar donde sea que estés."

msgctxt "428_Erena"
msgid "Wow! I don't play pachinko so I never knew about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "440_Akiyama"
msgid "Then it'd be good practice for the real thing. Why not try it out? You might get hooked."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "452_Erena"
msgid "Okay. I'll give it a whirl."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "464_Akiyama"
msgid "Ever heard of Amoebatar?"
msgstr "¿Has oído hablar de Amoebatar?"

msgctxt "476_Erena"
msgid "I heard the name somewhere before..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "488_Akiyama"
msgid "It's an online community that lets you create an avatar identical to yourself. Celebrities are even on it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "500_Erena"
msgid "Wow, that so? Maybe I'll check it out, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "512_Akiyama"
msgid "Hear about the ghost in the underground mall?"
msgstr "¿Escuchaste sobre el fantasma que hay en el centro comercial subterráneo?"

msgctxt "524_Erena"
msgid "Huh? A ghost!?"
msgstr "¿¡Eh!? ¿¡Un fantasma!?"

msgctxt "536_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah. When they were building the mall, a construction worker died in an accident."
msgstr "Sí. Dicen que cuando construían el centro comercial, uno de los que trabajaban en la obra murió en un accidente."

msgctxt "548_Akiyama"
msgid "Now, night after night, his ghost appears to wander the empty mall."
msgstr "Ahora, cuando cae la noche, su fantasma deambula por el centro comercial vacío."

msgctxt "560_Erena"
msgid "No way! I want to see it for myself!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "572_Akiyama"
msgid "That doesn't scare you in the least?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "584_Erena"
msgid "I watch a lot of horror movies. If ghosts really do exist, I'd like to see one just once."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "596_Akiyama"
msgid "Hear about the footbaths at Yunosono Hot Springs? You don't take off your clothes, so men and women can go in together."
msgstr "¿Has oído hablar de los baños de pies de las Aguas termales Yunosono? No hace falta que te quites la ropa, así que hombres y mujeres pueden entrar juntos."

msgctxt "608_Erena"
msgid "Oh? I have been feelin' lethargic lately. Maybe I should check it out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "620_Akiyama"
msgid "It's a lot easier than setting aside an entire day to go to some hot spring in the mountains. Try dropping by after work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "632_Erena"
msgid "That's a mighty fine idea. Thanks for tellin' me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "644_Akiyama"
msgid "Golf is getting pretty popular. A lot of couples go on golf dates nowadays."
msgstr "El golf se ha vuelto popular últimamente. Y al parecer las parejas van de citas a esos lugares."

msgctxt "656_Erena"
msgid "You don't say? People in Tokyo sure do date in style!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "668_Akiyama"
msgid "How about trying some golf? It's good exercise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "680_Erena"
msgid "True. Plus, playing golf for fun has this high-class feel to it, kinda like being a celebrity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "692_Akiyama"
msgid "Say, Erena, do you like liver? Liver contains this kind of acid that reverses aging in the brain."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "704_Erena"
msgid "I'm crazy about liver sashimi. I eat it all the time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "716_Akiyama"
msgid "It's good for your memory too, so you'll stay sharp when you're old."
msgstr "Es bueno para tu memoria, y dice que te ayudará a prevenir el deterioro mental por vejez."

msgctxt "728_Erena"
msgid "I'm not worried about that. I'm still young!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "740_Akiyama"
msgid "Heheh. You'd do well taking it down a notch from that hectic life you lead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "752_Akiyama"
msgid "Pole dancing is great for losing weight. You work your whole body, keeping you slim."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "764_Erena"
msgid "Pole dancin'? That's an erotic dance, right? Sounds like fun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "776_Akiyama"
msgid "You're already the flashy type. It matches you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "788_Erena"
msgid "You're right. I think I'll sleep on it."
msgstr "Tienes razón. Será mejor que piense en algo."

msgctxt "800_Akiyama"
msgid "Sweet sake is all the rage now. Women like to have it at Sushi Gin these days."
msgstr "Parece que últimamente el sake dulce está de moda. En Sushi Gin la mujeres lo piden regularmente junto a sus comidas."

msgctxt "812_Erena"
msgid "Really? I'm partial to shochu though, so I can hold my drink without ordering the sweet stuff."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "824_Akiyama"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "Ya veo..."

msgctxt "872_Akiyama"
msgid "So about 777 Town..."
msgstr "Acerca del 777 Town..."

msgctxt "884_Erena"
msgid "Oh, I played it the other day! It's a real blast. It's so fun, I don't think I'll ever need to go to a real pachinko parlor again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "896_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh. Sounds like you're really into it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "908_Akiyama"
msgid "So about Amoebatar..."
msgstr "Acerca del Amoebatar..."

msgctxt "920_Erena"
msgid "I tried it out, actually. I chatted with some friends back in Kyoto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "932_Erena"
msgid "My avatar looks just like me－really flashy! My friends knew who it was right off the bat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "944_Akiyama"
msgid "Heheh, I see."
msgstr "Je, je, je. Ya veo."

msgctxt "956_Akiyama"
msgid "So about that ghost in the underground mall..."
msgstr "Acerca del fantasma del centro comercial..."

msgctxt "968_Erena"
msgid "Oh, that. Any new developments? Is it for real?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "980_Akiyama"
msgid "Who knows? I sure wish I did."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "992_Erena"
msgid "What? So it could all be a hoax then? That's no fun..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1004_Akiyama"
msgid "Did you try out the footbaths at Yunosono?"
msgstr "¿Probaste los baños de pies en Yunosono?"

msgctxt "1016_Erena"
msgid "Yep! It was great! Hot springs really help take the edge off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1028_Erena"
msgid "You sure know some real neat places."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1040_Akiyama"
msgid "Heheh."
msgstr "Je, je, je."

msgctxt "1052_Akiyama"
msgid "About those golf dates..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1064_Erena"
msgid "Trampin' around a golf course might not be my thing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1076_Erena"
msgid "Hitting ball after ball at a practice range sounds like a lot more fun to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1088_Akiyama"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "Ya veo..."

msgctxt "1100_Akiyama"
msgid "Had any liver lately?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1112_Erena"
msgid "You bet. I eat it all the time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1124_Erena"
msgid "If it makes me any younger, I'll be back to being a high school girl before ya know it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1136_Akiyama"
msgid "Whoa now, it only works on your brain."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1148_Akiyama"
msgid "About that pole dancing workout..."
msgstr "Sobre hacer ejercicio con pole dance..."

msgctxt "1160_Erena"
msgid "I went to a dance studio to check it out. The pros really know how to work it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1172_Erena"
msgid "Watching from the sidelines was so satisfying, I ended up just goin' straight home afterwards."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1184_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh. I guess just being able to watch is worth the trip."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1196_Akiyama"
msgid "Did you try that sake we talked about? You know, the sweet kind?"
msgstr "¿Probaste el sake que te mencione? ¿El que era dulce?"

msgctxt "1208_Erena"
msgid "Huh? Me? I don't like that stuff, remember?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1220_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, that's right."
msgstr ""

